quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  6,132,"Ne boosi bali khutsingasi tsiawukhane khukalia kabakholanga. Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi shang’ang’alanga ehale khukabakholanga tawe."
  6,133,"Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Winyala, Owetsimbabaasi. Niyenya, nabawesiayo, ne arerao abandi baachamile abalali enywe tawe, shingala yabainia enywe okhurula mulwibulo olwa abandu bandi."
  6,134,"Ne toto kalia kamulakungwa kaliula, ne shimulinyala okhushila tawe."
  6,135,"Boola mbu; “Enywe abandu banje, khole akenyu mubunyali bwenyu, siesi ekholanga akanje. Ne mulitsa okhumanya mbu niwina uliba nende inzu indayi mubumalilishi. Toto ababii shibalibura tawe."
  6,136,"Ne bakholela Nyasaye ebuleka khumimela echia yaloonga, nende mumiruko, ne baboolanga mbu; “Ino niya Nyasaye,” khukhuboola khwabu butswa, “ne ino niya balia bakhutsokaasinjia Nyasaye ninabo.” Kho bilia ebisuubililwe abanyasaye babu, shibiulanga khu Nyasaye tawe, ne ebisuubililwe Nyasaye biulanga khubanyasaye babu. Ni amabii muno akababusinjia."
  6,137,"Ne khandi abanji mubatsokaasi abo baronelwa nende abasanji babu okhwira abana babu khulwa okhubasishia nende okhubanyasilia idini yabu. Ne Nyasaye achamanga, shibakhakholele bario tawe. Kho baleshe nende akabachikhanga ako."